# TLSNotary route — direct mode.
# No proxy route for TLSNotary; clients connect direct to the host port
# 7047. Use when upstream notary's WS handshake / framing rejects being
# behind a reverse proxy. The 'tlsnotary' compose service must still
# publish 7047 to the host in this mode (it does, by default).
#
# Selected when TLSNOTARY_PROXY_MODE=direct.

# Intentionally empty — handled by the host port mapping in compose.
